Beiersdorf’s Tesa to Make Pharmaceutical Plasters, FAZ Reports

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-04-01T06:10:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-01/beiersdorf-s-tesa-to-make-pharmaceutical-plasters-faz-reports.html
Beiersdorf AG (BEI) ’s Tesa unit will start
producing plasters that contain pharmaceutical ingredients in
the first quarter of next year, as the company enters the
pharmaceutical market to increase sales, the  Frankfurter
Allgemeine Zeitung  reported today, citing Thomas Schlegel, who
heads Tesa.  The likely market volume for the product is estimated at
1 billion euros ($1.4 billion), the newspaper cited Schlegel as
saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
